Food was just Subway as usual but.....walked in before ordering to use the restroom and saw a sign that says "restrooms for customers only" so I thought no problem since we were ordering anyway.  Asked the cashier to use the restroom and he gave me a coin.  No problem.  Once I opened that door..OH MY GOODNESS!! That restroom was the nastiest, dirtiest, restroom I have seen in a long time.  I'm talking about I would have rather used the restroom at a gas station or rest stop.  That thing was disgusting.  To top it off I was sooo disgusted I wanted to make sure I washed my hands and touched nothing but there was no soap or paper towels!! Yuck!!!!! If my boyfriend wouldn't have already ordered that food we would've been walking out end of story. I posted two pictures of the door lock and coin but didn't want to disgust you guys with pictures of that nasty bathroom. Do yourself a favor and skip this place altogether. Back home in Florida Subway restrooms are always clean............
